headline.main: France's Fillon Calls on Party to Unite Around Him
headline.print_headline: France's Fillon Calls on Party to Unite Around Him

lead_paragraph: Francois Fillon urged his conservative party on Monday to rally around him, saying he was the only legitimate candidate despite calls by many in his camp for him to pull out of the French presidential race over allegations of misuse of public funds.
